Package org.eclipse.m2m.atl.core.service

Class CoreService

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.m2m.atl.core.service.CoreService
public final class CoreService extends Object
The CoreService utility class provides a way to use extension points in order to retrieve the needed extensions:
  • ILauncher
  • IInjector
  • IExtractor
  • ModelFactory
For each extension class type, a method returns the list of all detected extensions names.
